{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":"2026-03-05T14:37:30.875Z","tool_name":"replace","tool_id":"replace_1772721450875_0","parameters":{"instruction":"Update HandleEvent to use Branch from bellows.PREvent.","old_string":"// HandleEvent processes a Bellows PR event and dispatches any required actions.\nfunc (m *Manager) HandleEvent(ctx context.Context, event bellows.PREvent) {\n\tm.mu.Lock()\n\tst, ok := m.states[event.PRNumber]\n\tif !ok {\n\t\tst = &PRState{\n\t\t\tPRNumber: event.PRNumber,\n\t\t\tBeadID:   event.BeadID,\n\t\t\tAnvil:    event.Anvil,\n\t\t}\n\t\tm.states[event.PRNumber] = st\n\t}\n\tm.mu.Unlock()\n","new_string":"// HandleEvent processes a Bellows PR event and dispatches any required actions.\nfunc (m *Manager) HandleEvent(ctx context.Context, event bellows.PREvent) {\n\tm.mu.Lock()\n\tst, ok := m.states[event.PRNumber]\n\tif !ok {\n\t\tst = &PRState{\n\t\t\tPRNumber: event.PRNumber,\n\t\t\tBeadID:   event.BeadID,\n\t\t\tAnvil:    event.Anvil,\n\t\t\tBranch:   event.Branch,\n\t\t}\n\t\tm.states[event.PRNumber] = st\n\t}\n\tif event.Branch != \"\" {\n\t\tst.Branch = event.Branch\n\t}\n\tm.mu.Unlock()\n","file_path":"c:\\source\\fhigit\\Forge\\.workers\\Forge-7ug\\internal\\lifecycle\\lifecycle.go","allow_multiple":false}}
